SUMMARY:Francisco Dominguez Presentation of  Photographs of Gaza War Protests
DESCRIPTION:Francisco Dominguez will present a slide show of his photographs documenting the protests against Israel’s war on Gaza. Francisco Dominguez will also speak about the protest movement against the Gaza War. \nFrancisco Dominguez is a Sacramento-based documentary photographer\, artist\, and printmaker specializing in social justice\, labor movements\, protests\, civil rights\, and indigenous peoples. His work has been acquired by institutions like the UC Davis Library. He also hosts a public affairs program on KDVS radio.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/francisco-dominguez-presentation-of-photographs-of-gaza-war-protests/
LOCATION:Friends Meetinghouse\, 345 L St\, Davis\, 345 L St\, Davis\, CA\, 95616
CATEGORIES:Art
