UID:10074269-1773947400-1773953100@thedirt.online
SUMMARY:Photography Club of Davis
DESCRIPTION:The Photography Club of Davis will meet on Thursday\, March 19\, at 7:10pm in the Blanchard Room of the Mary L. Stephens Library at 314 East 14th Street in Davis. The meeting will feature a photo critique of member-submitted images. Critiques tend to be positive learning experiences for both submitters and the general audience. Participants discuss “why does this image work” as well as “why does this image not work” and how the image may be improved. Attendees also learn about the techniques involved. The Photography Club of Davis meets every month on the third Thursday of the month (except July and August) and welcomes members of the public to attend. \n“This event is not sponsored by Yolo County Library and the presence of this group in the meeting room does not constitute Yolo County Library’s endorsement of the policies or beliefs of this group.”
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/photography-club-of-davis/
LOCATION:Mary L. Stephens Davis Branch Library Blanchard Room\, 315 E 14th St\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/succulents.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Photography Club of Davis":MAILTO:photographyclubofdavis@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
