DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T160000
SUMMARY:Gel Printing Workshop with Sara Post
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nUnder the guidance of artist Sara Po
 st\, students will explore the ins and out of gel printing. Participants w
 ill experiment with layering\, masks\, stencils\, and other gel printing t
 echniques\, as well as work with a variety of papers. Gel prints\, beautif
 ul in themselves\, are also a wonderful way to make handmade papers for co
 llage or under layers for painting. Students will leave this class with a 
 portfolio of prints to display on their own or to use in making other artw
 orks.\n\nGel Printing Workshop with Sara Post\nSaturday\, March 21\, 9:30 
 AM - 4 PM\n$170 Members\, $190 Non-Members (Materials not included)\n\n**R
 egistration is required in advance through the Pence's website ([CLICK HER
 E](https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/)).**
 \n\nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/pence-adult-art-programs/events/31328
 7945/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260210T003150Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260210T003150Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
