 ary 2–3\, 2026** (New Year) and **April 3–4\, 2026** (Easter).\n2. **S
 pecial Gatherings (Tentative):**\n**• February 14\, 2026:** Valentine’
 s Day & pre–Lunar New Year celebration in person at Phoenix Hall\, 2nd F
 loor\, Davis Community Church.\n**• March 14\, 2026:** Additional in-per
 son gathering (tentative).\n\n**Return to In-Person Meetings:**\nWe will r
 esume our **regular in-person gatherings on April 11\, 2026** at the **2nd
  floor rooms of Phoenix Hall\, Davis Community Church**.\n\nFor more infor
 mation about Intercultural Mosaics classes and activities\, visit **[www.n
 extg.org](http://www.nextg.org)** or contact **Dr. Stephen Moon** at **916
 -217-5470** or **catalyst@nextg.org**.
