  the Loose is an award-winning early literacy program for toddlers (ages 2
 -3) and their grown-ups.  It combines music\, movement\, rhymes\, and boo
 ks to help young children develop language skills\, social and emotional s
 kills\, general knowledge about the world\, and a love of learning.\n\nEve
 ry Tuesday in the Blanchard Room of the Mary L. Stephens Davis Branch Lib
 rary.
