SUMMARY:Barrel Tasting and Tour
DESCRIPTION:🍷 Barrel Tasting & Tour at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis 🍷\nFriday\, March 27 | 4:00 PM \nEver wondered what our wines taste like before they hit the bottle? This is your chance to find out—and it’s a pretty special one. \nJoin us for an intimate Barrel Tasting & Tour\, where you’ll sip\, stroll\, and sneak behind the scenes at Great Bear Vineyards. This rare experience includes a guided flight of five wines\, with select tastes straight from the barrel—yes\, the barrel! You’ll be led by one of our owners\, winemakers\, or senior wine educators as they share stories\, secrets\, and the craft behind our award-winning\, estate-grown wines. \n✨ Your ticket includes:\n• Flight of 5 wines\n• Barrel samples (a rare treat!)\n• Vineyard walk & behind-the-scenes barrel room tour\n• Insider knowledge from the people who make the wine \nAnd because it’s Friday… we’re keeping the party going! 🎶🍕\nStick around for Friday-Fest with live jazz from the Potential Jazz Ensemble and delicious wood-fired pizza from Italian Brother’s Pizza. \nCome for the barrels\, stay for the vibes. We can’t wait to welcome you! 🍷🔥
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/barrel-tasting-and-tour/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/3-27-Barrel-Tasting-Thumbnail-q0Hr3I.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Davis": "https://visitdavis.org/event/friday-fest/", "Visit Yolo": "https://visityolo.com/event/friday-fest/"}
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Davis": "https://visitdavis.org/event/friday-fest/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitdavis
X-SOURCE:Visit Davis, Visit Yolo
X-SOURCE-URL:https://visitdavis.org/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T200000
DTSTAMP:20260319T194359
CREATED:20260128T234243Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T022653Z
UID:10002793-1774630800-1774641600@visitdavis.org
SUMMARY:Friday-Fest
DESCRIPTION:🎷🍕 Friday-Fest at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis 🍷🎶\nFriday\, March 27 | 5–8 PM \nLive Music Friday’s are back! Join us for Friday-Fest\, featuring live jazz from the Potential Jazz Ensemble and fresh\, wood-fired pizza from Italian Brother’s Pizza. Your ticket includes a glass of wine and live music—the perfect pairing. \n🍕 Food starts at 5 PM with authentic\, made-to-order pizzas hot from the wood-fired oven.\n🎶 Live music from 6–7:30 PM\, with the Potential Jazz Ensemble bringing vibrant\, feel-good jazz that blends classic roots with modern creativity. Expect smooth grooves\, lively solos\, and great energy from this talented lineup of sax\, bass\, guitar\, piano\, and percussion. \nCome early\, grab a slice\, sip some wine\, and settle in for a relaxed\, delicious evening at the vineyard. Weekend vibes start here! 🍷✨
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/friday-fest/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Highway128PressTrip_GreatBearVineyards_2024_MaxWhittaker_12-Copy-scaled-OoIRnT.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
