DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T150000
UID:2cc9cee0a4999c450f7a613d871403de@events.yolocountylibrary.org
DESCRIPTION:Welcome trainers\, to Pokémon Club! Pokémon club meets every
  Wednesday to share in the love of Pokémon. Come participate in activitie
 s and learn to play the trading card game\, and even take down powerful Po
 kémon in Raids! Materials are provided. Participants may bring their own 
