DESCRIPTION:Meet in front of the Davis  Vets center on 14th st at 11:00am
  on Tuesdays.\nWe will decide where to go for lunch based on the input fro
 m riders.   \nWoodland\, Winters and Dixon are the usual destinations. 
   The pace is pretty relaxed\, usually 14-15 mph\, with  occasional regr
 oups. \n\n\nThanks\, David Joshel\nPhone 530-400-3288
LAST-MODIFIED:20260303T230350Z
LOCATION:City of Davis: Veterans Memorial Center\, 203 E 14th St\, Davis\,
  CA 95616\, USA
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-SOURCE:Davis Bike Club
END:VEVENT
